# Quickstart Demo - Combined essential workflow
Output ../screenshots/quickstart.gif
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set PlaybackSpeed 1.0
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

# Clear screen and show prompt
Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

# Title
